house mimicking candlelight.

00:19:04.310 --> 00:19:08.640 align:middle line:84%
And I do have that
pattern a lot of times.

00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:10.640 align:middle line:84%
First sleep, and then
wake up about 3:00 or 4:00

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:11.700 align:middle line:90%
