dreams come through,

00:19:20.990 --> 00:19:22.460 align:middle line:90%
which is in the second sleep.

00:19:22.460 --> 00:19:23.600 align:middle line:90%
>> BROWN: Right.

00:19:23.600 --> 00:19:25.010 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: But I agree with you.

