feeling of anxiety and fear

00:23:52.110 --> 00:23:54.690 align:middle line:84%
that was rippling out
through the congregation.

00:23:54.690 --> 00:23:58.200 align:middle line:84%
And everyone knew that it
was just a matter of time

00:23:58.200 --> 00:24:02.190 align:middle line:84%
