tapping into something

00:24:45.900 --> 00:24:49.710 align:middle line:10%
like what Carl Jung would call
the collective unconscious.

00:24:49.710 --> 00:24:51.840 align:middle line:10%
It was some kind of
universal, big dream

00:24:51.840 --> 00:24:53.190 align:middle line:10%
that I was tapping into.

00:24:53.190 --> 00:24:56.550 align:middle line:84%
But the most remarkable thing,
