talking to them.

00:25:59.400 --> 00:26:01.800 align:middle line:84%
And when you start talking
to them, I mean, some of them

00:26:01.800 --> 00:26:05.520 align:middle line:84%
seem a little bit robotic
and not very bright.

00:26:05.520 --> 00:26:10.590 align:middle line:84%
Others seem as
independently-minded as you

00:26:10.590 --> 00:26:13.230 align:middle line:84%
and I seem, and it's very,
very compellingly real

00:26:13.230 --> 00:26:15.270 align:middle line:84%
and it's very hard to
think that they're not

00:26:15.270 --> 00:26:17.430 align:middle line:90%
an actual, living intelligence.

00:26:17.430 --> 00:26:19.170 align:middle line:84%
And then you encounter
these other beings

00:26:19.170 --> 00:26:21.090 align:middle line:84%
that seem to know a
whole lot more about you

00:26:21.090 --> 00:26:22.080 align:middle line:90%
than you know yourself.

00:26:22.080 --> 00:26:23.970 align:middle line:84%
And I recall there
was the spiritual,

00:26:23.970 --> 00:26:25.500 align:middle line:90%
or the wise, masters.

00:26:25.500 --> 00:26:27.330 align:middle line:84%
And you can encounter
this whole range

00:26:27.330 --> 00:26:30.450 align:middle line:84%
of beings inside of a
lucid dream or inside

00:26:30.450 --> 00:26:31.860 align:middle line:90%
of a shamanic experience.

00:26:31.860 --> 00:26:33.040 align:middle line:90%
It's very similar.

00:26:33.040 --> 00:26:35.700 align:middle line:84%
And what I found
even more powerful

00:26:35.700 --> 00:26:38.130 align:middle line:84%
than talking to the
dream characters

00:26:38.130 --> 00:26:40.530 align:middle line:90%
is to talk to the dream itself.

00:26:40.530 --> 00:26:42.150 align:middle line:84%
To just simply ignore
the environment,

00:26:42.150 --> 00:26:44.250 align:middle line:84%
to ignore the
characters, and to simply

00:26:44.250 --> 00:26:46.800 align:middle line:84%
lift your head to the sky
and just ask a question

00:26:46.800 --> 00:26:47.760 align:middle line:90%
to the dream.

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:50.280 align:middle line:84%
And surprisingly,
something responds.

00:26:50.280 --> 00:26:51.630 align:middle line:90%
The dream responds.

00:26:51.630 --> 00:26:54.720 align:middle line:84%
And it will respond either by
speaking to you in English,

00:26:54.720 --> 00:26:56.640 align:middle line:84%
or by changing the
scenery of the dream

00:26:56.640 --> 00:26:58.620 align:middle line:90%
around in some kind of way.

00:26:58.620 --> 00:26:59.760 align:middle line:90%
But it does respond.

00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:01.790 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes it doesn't
respond in that dream.

00:27:01.790 --> 00:27:04.850 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes it'll respond
several dreams later.

00:27:04.850 --> 00:27:06.480 align:middle line:90%
But it does respond to you.

00:27:06.480 --> 00:27:08.121 align:middle line:90%
And who is it that's responding?

00:27:08.121 --> 00:27:09.120 align:middle line:90%
That's the big question.

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:11.340 align:middle line:90%
Is your unconscious mind?

00:27:11.340 --> 00:27:14.430 align:middle line:84%
Is it one of these
daemons or one

00:27:14.430 --> 00:27:17.220 align:middle line:84%
of these other intelligences
that the Greeks believed

00:27:17.220 --> 00:27:21.990 align:middle line:84%
that we were communicating
with, one of these spirits?

00:27:21.990 --> 00:27:25.950 align:middle line:84%
I try, in my book,
not to adhere myself

00:27:25.950 --> 00:27:27.916 align:middle line:84%
to any one particular
belief system,

00:27:27.916 --> 00:27:29.790 align:middle line:84%
but try to show the
different belief systems.

00:27:29.790 --> 00:27:31.207 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Just
the possibilities.

00:27:31.207 --> 00:27:33.290 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: Could be any
number one of those things.

00:27:33.290 --> 00:27:35.250 align:middle line:84%
But whatever it is,
there is the ability

00:27:35.250 --> 00:27:37.750 align:middle line:84%
to communicate with these
beings or with this higher self,

00:27:37.750 --> 00:27:39.495 align:middle line:90%
and it is very, very compelling.

00:27:39.495 --> 00:27:41.370 align:middle line:84%
And they will teach you
things about yourself

00:27:41.370 --> 00:27:42.490 align:middle line:90%
that you don't already know.

00:27:42.490 --> 00:27:44.156 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Absolutely
If I get messages,

00:27:44.156 --> 00:27:45.300 align:middle line:90%
there's a particular voice.

00:27:45.300 --> 00:27:48.090 align:middle line:84%
And if I hear that voice
telling me something in a dream,

00:27:48.090 --> 00:27:50.490 align:middle line:84%
then I better pay attention,
because it's always

00:27:50.490 --> 00:27:53.770 align:middle line:84%
a heads up that I really
needed at the time.

00:27:53.770 --> 00:27:58.080 align:middle line:84%
And so that, to me,
is very sacred--

00:27:58.080 --> 00:28:00.660 align:middle line:84%
those relationships that
we have in dream time.

00:28:00.660 --> 00:28:04.280 align:middle line:84%
Especially when you have, again,
I think a trusted relationship

00:28:04.280 --> 00:28:05.910 align:middle line:90%
that-- it's tried and true.

00:28:05.910 --> 00:28:08.820 align:middle line:84%
Where you've seen the validity,
you've seen it bear out.

00:28:08.820 --> 00:28:10.530 align:middle line:84%
You can develop a
lot of confidence

00:28:10.530 --> 00:28:11.940 align:middle line:90%
once you realize that--

00:28:11.940 --> 00:28:15.580 align:middle line:84%
ah, last time that happened,
this exactly happened.

00:28:15.580 --> 00:28:16.380 align:middle line:90%
It did go that way.

00:28:16.380 --> 00:28:18.460 align:middle line:84%
I'm glad I listened,
and so forth.

00:28:18.460 --> 00:28:21.420 align:middle line:84%
So those are relationships to
develop trust between, just

00:28:21.420 --> 00:28:23.290 align:middle line:90%
like on Earth, right?

00:28:23.290 --> 00:28:24.630 align:middle line:90%
>> BROWN: Exactly.

00:28:24.630 --> 00:28:25.950 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: What about the
notion-- oh, I'm sorry.

00:28:25.950 --> 00:28:26.790 align:middle line:84%
Did you have something
more on that?

00:28:26.790 --> 00:28:27.330 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: I was
just going to say--

00:28:27.330 --> 00:28:29.121 align:middle line:84%
that sort of trust that
builds up, I think,

00:28:29.121 --> 00:28:33.080 align:middle line:84%
is very important, because
people actually ask me about,

00:28:33.080 --> 00:28:34.860 align:middle line:84%
when you encounter
one of these entities,

00:28:34.860 --> 00:28:36.120 align:middle line:90%
how should you relate to them?

00:28:36.120 --> 00:28:37.830 align:middle line:84%
And I always say,
just like you would

00:28:37.830 --> 00:28:40.560 align:middle line:84%
relate to any other person
that you actually meet,

00:28:40.560 --> 00:28:41.700 align:middle line:90%
any other stranger.

00:28:41.700 --> 00:28:43.380 align:middle line:84%
I mean, don't
immediately trust them.

00:28:43.380 --> 00:28:45.319 align:middle line:90%
Be skeptical of what they say.

00:28:45.319 --> 00:28:46.860 align:middle line:84%
Don't assume that
everything they say

00:28:46.860 --> 00:28:49.500 align:middle line:84%
is going to be
God-given advice to you.

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:53.340 align:middle line:84%
But be very open to it and
take it in and with time,

00:28:53.340 --> 00:28:55.300 align:middle line:84%
when you see they're
right and they make sense,

00:28:55.300 --> 00:28:56.970 align:middle line:84%
then you can build
up a sense of trust.

00:28:56.970 --> 00:28:59.490 align:middle line:84%
And that happens over
time with these entities.

00:28:59.490 --> 00:29:00.600 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:29:00.600 --> 00:29:02.830 align:middle line:84%
And we've got to look at
the other entities, as well.

00:29:02.830 --> 00:29:08.580 align:middle line:84%
I mean, in dream time, as
with using other substances

00:29:08.580 --> 00:29:12.120 align:middle line:84%
and hallucinogens, it
is every bit as likely

00:29:12.120 --> 00:29:15.510 align:middle line:84%
a person will start
interfacing with lower realms.

00:29:15.510 --> 00:29:19.110 align:middle line:84%
And lower realms
can be tricksters.

00:29:19.110 --> 00:29:20.590 align:middle line:84%
Lot of tricky stuff
going on there.

00:29:20.590 --> 00:29:21.390 align:middle line:90%
>> BROWN: Right.

00:29:21.390 --> 00:29:23.740 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Let's talk about that
interface with darker realms,

00:29:23.740 --> 00:29:24.370 align:middle line:90%
as well.

00:29:24.370 --> 00:29:26.703 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: Well, that's why I
tell people to be skeptical

00:29:26.703 --> 00:29:29.220 align:middle line:84%
and to not always believe
everything you hear when

00:29:29.220 --> 00:29:30.600 align:middle line:84%
you're encountering
these beings.

00:29:30.600 --> 00:29:33.152 align:middle line:84%
I mean, who knows, really,
what their origin is

00:29:33.152 --> 00:29:35.610 align:middle line:84%
or what their intentions are
or whether they have your best

00:29:35.610 --> 00:29:37.200 align:middle line:90%
intentions at heart?

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:40.560 align:middle line:84%
So I think it's very
important to always maintain

00:29:40.560 --> 00:29:42.825 align:middle line:84%
a certain degree of
skepticism with these beings.

00:29:42.825 --> 00:29:44.700 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And the
discernment process, then,

00:29:44.700 --> 00:29:46.124 align:middle line:90%
becomes critical.

00:29:46.124 --> 00:29:47.790 align:middle line:84%
Even when you're
sleeping, discernment--

00:29:47.790 --> 00:29:51.630 align:middle line:84%
if you're programming
your mind to become aware

00:29:51.630 --> 00:29:53.925 align:middle line:84%
and become discerning
even during dream time.

00:29:53.925 --> 00:29:56.910 align:middle line:84%
Which then, of course, leads to
a certain amount of lucidity.

00:29:56.910 --> 00:30:00.600 align:middle line:84%
But my observation
is really simple.

00:30:00.600 --> 00:30:03.480 align:middle line:84%
If you have any
kind of being that's

00:30:03.480 --> 00:30:07.380 align:middle line:84%
perpetuating fearful
circumstance of any kind

00:30:07.380 --> 00:30:10.800 align:middle line:84%
or controlling or
demanding something of you

00:30:10.800 --> 00:30:16.080 align:middle line:84%
or hierarchical, then I
will, without question,

00:30:16.080 --> 00:30:18.930 align:middle line:84%
assume that this is
a lower realm that's

00:30:18.930 --> 00:30:21.370 align:middle line:84%
trying to intrude upon
someone's consciousness.

00:30:21.370 --> 00:30:22.170 align:middle line:90%
Period.

00:30:22.170 --> 00:30:22.980 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: I think
that's a good gauge.

00:30:22.980 --> 00:30:24.021 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Really simple.

00:30:24.021 --> 00:30:26.130 align:middle line:84%
If it's not
empowering, if it's not

00:30:26.130 --> 00:30:28.920 align:middle line:84%
lifting you up, encouraging,
giving permission,

00:30:28.920 --> 00:30:30.339 align:middle line:84%
you're dealing
with lower realms.

00:30:30.339 --> 00:30:32.130 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: I think, in
general, that's true.

00:30:32.130 --> 00:30:33.990 align:middle line:10%
There is something to
be said for the fact

00:30:33.990 --> 00:30:37.366 align:middle line:10%
that some of these people have
to confront traumas in order

00:30:37.366 --> 00:30:38.490 align:middle line:10%
to grow during the process.

00:30:38.490 --> 00:30:40.198 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And they
can show up that way,

00:30:40.198 --> 00:30:43.560 align:middle line:84%
to make you aware enough to know
that there is that issue there

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:46.290 align:middle line:90%
that must still be transformed.

00:30:46.290 --> 00:30:49.770 align:middle line:84%
And I think in that case,
that's where lower realms really

00:30:49.770 --> 00:30:52.560 align:middle line:90%
serve their function well.

00:30:52.560 --> 00:30:56.280 align:middle line:84%
And we tend to put everything
that's of a little bit darker,

00:30:56.280 --> 00:30:59.380 align:middle line:84%
scarier, lower in--
and again, that's

00:30:59.380 --> 00:31:00.630 align:middle line:90%
hierarchical even saying that.

00:31:00.630 --> 00:31:03.300 align:middle line:84%
But darker, so to speak,
or more uncomfortable.

00:31:03.300 --> 00:31:05.520 align:middle line:90%
We tend to demonize that.

00:31:05.520 --> 00:31:07.720 align:middle line:84%
And they're called daemons,
as a matter of fact.

00:31:07.720 --> 00:31:10.410 align:middle line:84%
But the reality is they're
showing up for a reason.

00:31:10.410 --> 00:31:12.180 align:middle line:84%
There's something
unhealed, something

00:31:12.180 --> 00:31:14.950 align:middle line:84%
that needs transforming, or
they wouldn't be showing up

00:31:14.950 --> 00:31:16.480 align:middle line:90%
on that dreamscape.

00:31:16.480 --> 00:31:18.480 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: Yeah, I think
everything that shows up

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:21.360 align:middle line:84%
in our dreams is there
because it needs healing.

00:31:21.360 --> 00:31:24.310 align:middle line:84%
It needs to be recognized
at this particular time.

00:31:24.310 --> 00:31:27.510 align:middle line:84%
So I think that it's very
important to recognize and take

00:31:27.510 --> 00:31:29.600 align:middle line:84%
account for everything
you experience right now.

00:31:29.600 --> 00:31:31.950 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And so talk about
feelings in dream time,

00:31:31.950 --> 00:31:36.360 align:middle line:84%
because the notion that a dream
can have all these symbols,

00:31:36.360 --> 00:31:38.439 align:middle line:84%
symbols are different
for everybody.

00:31:38.439 --> 00:31:40.230 align:middle line:84%
What a squirrel is to
one person in a dream

00:31:40.230 --> 00:31:41.280 align:middle line:90%
it's not to the other person.

00:31:41.280 --> 00:31:42.080 align:middle line:90%
>> BROWN: Right.

00:31:42.080 --> 00:31:44.220 align:middle line:84%
It's different for every
person, but every person

00:31:44.220 --> 00:31:46.560 align:middle line:84%
should be able to recognize
what it means to them.

00:31:46.560 --> 00:31:47.976 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's
what I'm saying.

00:31:47.976 --> 00:31:50.280 align:middle line:84%
That's where feelings really
come in in dream time.

00:31:50.280 --> 00:31:52.440 align:middle line:84%
How did that experience
make you feel?

00:31:52.440 --> 00:31:55.740 align:middle line:84%
You say the feline character,
you woke up sweating.

00:31:55.740 --> 00:31:59.550 align:middle line:84%
It was a very disturbing dream
about these controlling forces

00:31:59.550 --> 00:32:02.460 align:middle line:84%
that were, again, these
lower realms demanding

00:32:02.460 --> 00:32:03.980 align:middle line:90%
blood sacrifice--

00:32:03.980 --> 00:32:05.970 align:middle line:90%
really low stuff.

00:32:05.970 --> 00:32:08.970 align:middle line:84%
But it was very clear,
and that sense of relief--

00:32:08.970 --> 00:32:10.870 align:middle line:84%
and there's a lesson
in that, right?

00:32:10.870 --> 00:32:12.300 align:middle line:90%
Well, at least it wasn't me.

00:32:12.300 --> 00:32:14.360 align:middle line:84%
Everything's OK in
the world, right?

00:32:14.360 --> 00:32:15.160 align:middle line:90%
In that one.

00:32:15.160 --> 00:32:17.690 align:middle line:84%
Everyone breathed
a sigh of relief.

00:32:17.690 --> 00:32:20.530 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: I mean, I took
that dream, by the way,

00:32:20.530 --> 00:32:24.600 align:middle line:84%
as evidence for the origin
of religion, basically.

00:32:24.600 --> 00:32:27.100 align:middle line:84%
That religion, that there were
a lot of animal sacrifices

00:32:27.100 --> 00:32:30.204 align:middle line:84%
at the beginning of
religions, and why was that?

00:32:30.204 --> 00:32:31.620 align:middle line:84%
And it led me to
a lot of insight.

00:32:31.620 --> 00:32:33.610 align:middle line:84%
I spoke to Rupert
Sheldrake, actually.

00:32:33.610 --> 00:32:35.040 align:middle line:84%
I described in my
book, actually--

00:32:35.040 --> 00:32:36.623 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: What did
he say about that?

00:32:36.623 --> 00:32:40.830 align:middle line:10%
>> BROWN: He said that he
thought that the dream that I

00:32:40.830 --> 00:32:45.510 align:middle line:10%
had in Israel was representative
of what he had read in Barbara

00:32:45.510 --> 00:32:47.970 align:middle line:10%
Ehrenreich's book
called "Blood Rites"

00:32:47.970 --> 00:32:52.050 align:middle line:10%
about how in early
human societies,

00:32:52.050 --> 00:32:54.840 align:middle line:10%
we were often the
prey of animals--

00:32:54.840 --> 00:32:56.250 align:middle line:10%
of wildcats.

00:32:56.250 --> 00:32:59.310 align:middle line:84%
And we recognized
that because one of us

00:32:59.310 --> 00:33:02.550 align:middle line:84%
had to be sacrificed for
the wildcat to be satiated--

00:33:02.550 --> 00:33:06.150 align:middle line:84%
that once it was satiated,
it would then leave us alone.

00:33:06.150 --> 00:33:08.910 align:middle line:84%
And it would also
kill other prey.

00:33:08.910 --> 00:33:13.320 align:middle line:84%
It would kill other animals
that we would then harvest from.

00:33:13.320 --> 00:33:14.190 align:middle line:90%
We would then eat.

00:33:14.190 --> 00:33:17.500 align:middle line:84%
So it was providing for us and
also taking one of our own.

00:33:17.500 --> 00:33:20.100 align:middle line:84%
And Barbara Ehrenreich
and Rupert Sheldrake

00:33:20.100 --> 00:33:22.560 align:middle line:84%
told me that they
thought that this

00:33:22.560 --> 00:33:25.710 align:middle line:84%
may have had an influence on
the development of religion.

00:33:25.710 --> 00:33:30.210 align:middle line:84%
And Rupert saw that dream as
being some type of evidence

00:33:30.210 --> 00:33:31.890 align:middle line:90%
for that type of idea.

00:33:31.890 --> 00:33:34.300 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Interesting.

00:33:34.300 --> 00:33:39.720 align:middle line:90%
So I also have come to--

00:33:39.720 --> 00:33:42.150 align:middle line:84%
I don't think it's fair
to say a belief, but maybe

00:33:42.150 --> 00:33:43.650 align:middle line:84%
my current
understanding, because it

00:33:43.650 --> 00:33:44.994 align:middle line:90%
morphs as I have new evidence.

00:33:44.994 --> 00:33:47.160 align:middle line:84%
If you're open-minded,
everything's morphing, right?

00:33:47.160 --> 00:33:49.080 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: Yeah, you're
entertaining ideas.

00:33:49.080 --> 00:33:50.330 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Entertaining ideas.

00:33:50.330 --> 00:33:52.140 align:middle line:84%
I'm entertaining
this idea that when

00:33:52.140 --> 00:33:56.130 align:middle line:84%
we look back at some of the work
that we feature here at Gaia--

00:33:56.130 --> 00:33:59.220 align:middle line:84%
the work of Zecharia Sitchin
and Erich von Daniken

00:33:59.220 --> 00:34:02.820 align:middle line:84%
and others that have
basically run off

00:34:02.820 --> 00:34:04.980 align:middle line:90%
with the Anunnaki story.

00:34:04.980 --> 00:34:06.570 align:middle line:90%
Which is a pixel of history.

00:34:06.570 --> 00:34:09.330 align:middle line:84%
I mean, there are a lot of other
influences far prior to that,

00:34:09.330 --> 00:34:11.400 align:middle line:90%
but even so.

00:34:11.400 --> 00:34:16.139 align:middle line:84%
When again you start looking at
the intrusion, or corruption,

00:34:16.139 --> 00:34:18.510 align:middle line:90%
of the message upon humanity--

00:34:18.510 --> 00:34:22.860 align:middle line:84%
that there are these
demanding, wrathful gods--

00:34:22.860 --> 00:34:27.380 align:middle line:84%
which has been perpetuated
in Sunday school to this day,

00:34:27.380 --> 00:34:28.409 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:34:28.409 --> 00:34:31.199 align:middle line:84%
In all of the
Abrahamic traditions.

00:34:31.199 --> 00:34:32.850 align:middle line:84%
When you have that
overlay that's

00:34:32.850 --> 00:34:38.130 align:middle line:84%
now been perpetuated in our
soul group and tribal families

00:34:38.130 --> 00:34:40.889 align:middle line:90%
as stories, it's in our DNA.

00:34:40.889 --> 00:34:43.739 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's in
our spiritual DNA.

00:34:43.739 --> 00:34:47.190 align:middle line:84%
That has to be having a
tremendously negative impact

00:34:47.190 --> 00:34:49.110 align:middle line:84%
on humanity in their
dream time, as well.

00:34:49.110 --> 00:34:54.310 align:middle line:84%
Like you say-- sacrifices,
these fearful entities.

00:34:54.310 --> 00:34:56.050 align:middle line:84%
These entities that
are to be feared.

00:34:56.050 --> 00:34:58.300 align:middle line:84%
>> BROWN: Right, right--
these religious institutions.

00:34:58.300 --> 00:35:00.883 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's why I bring
it up, is because you said that.

00:35:00.883 --> 00:35:02.550 align:middle line:84%
I think that the
religious institutions

00:35:02.550 --> 00:35:05.350 align:middle line:84%
are hugely responsible for
the amount of anxiety and fear

00:35:05.350 --> 00:35:06.150 align:middle line:90%
in dreams.

00:35:06.150 --> 00:35:07.608 align:middle line:84%
If you just start
off with the fact

00:35:07.608 --> 00:35:10.560 align:middle line:84%
that you have to please
