happening when someone's astral

00:43:12.180 --> 00:43:13.050 align:middle line:90%
traveling.

00:43:13.050 --> 00:43:16.170 align:middle line:84%
But certainly, out-of-body
experiences and lucid dream

00:43:16.170 --> 00:43:18.810 align:middle line:84%
experiences-- there's a lot
of crossover between the two

00:43:18.810 --> 00:43:21.030 align:middle line:90%
types of phenomena.

00:43:21.030 --> 00:43:24.537 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Another somewhat--

00:43:24.537 --> 00:43:26.370 align:middle line:84%
