00:44:31.260 --> 00:44:34.710 align:middle line:84%
than us, and that are probably
eager to communicate with us

00:44:34.710 --> 00:44:36.960 align:middle line:90%
once we get there.

00:44:36.960 --> 00:44:39.180 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It seems, though,
