00:47:28.960 --> 00:47:30.650 align:middle line:84%
but also some of
your own experiences.

00:47:30.650 --> 00:47:31.450 align:middle line:90%
>> BROWN: Yeah.

00:47:31.450 --> 00:47:32.408 align:middle line:90%
Isn't that fascinating?

00:47:32.408 --> 00:47:34.770 align:middle line:84%
