of the stories that I recounted

00:48:08.170 --> 00:48:13.000 align:middle line:84%
was from someone who described
having a very serious infection

00:48:13.000 --> 00:48:14.110 align:middle line:90%
in their tonsils.

00:48:14.110 --> 00:48:16.540 align:middle line:84%
