I'm going to try to heal this.

00:48:25.960 --> 00:48:27.495 align:middle line:90%
So they went over to a mirror.

00:48:27.495 --> 00:48:28.870 align:middle line:84%
They stood in
front of the mirror

00:48:28.870 --> 00:48:32.470 align:middle line:84%
and they imagined a
glowing light just coming

00:48:32.470 --> 00:48:35.344 align:middle line:84%
from around their neck-- just
imagined this glowing light.

00:48:35.344 --> 00:48:37.510 align:middle line:84%
And they felt like there
was some kind of shift that

00:48:37.510 --> 00:48:40.180 align:middle line:84%
was going on during the
dream, and just imagine that.

00:48:40.180 --> 00:48:41.830 align:middle line:84%
