up, remarkably, they

00:48:41.830 --> 00:48:45.730 align:middle line:84%
reported that 95%
of the infection

00:48:45.730 --> 00:48:47.500 align:middle line:90%
had healed during that time.

00:48:47.500 --> 00:48:49.670 align:middle line:90%
So it's really quite remarkable.

00:48:49.670 --> 00:48:51.520 align:middle line:84%
This is really something
that really should

00:48:51.520 --> 00:48:52.840 align:middle line:90%
be researched a whole lot more.

00:48:52.840 --> 00:48:53.756 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:48:53.756 --> 00:48:55.450 align:middle line:84%
Have you played
with it yourself?

00:48:55.450 --> 00:48:57.610 align:middle line:84%
